#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_asset_leasing
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_asset_rental
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding:0px;\">\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('customer') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    I hope this email finds you well. We are pleased to confirm the leasing arrangement for the\n"
"                    following asset:\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Asset Name:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    Lease Start Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('start_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Lease End Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('end_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    As per the agreement, please ensure timely payment of the lease fees and adhere to the terms\n"
"                    outlined therein.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Should you have any questions or require further clarification regarding the lease\n"
"                    agreement, feel free to contact us at your convenience.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div style = \"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"<div>\n"
"Cher\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('client') ou not_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"J'espère que cet e-mail vous trouve bien.Nous sommes heureux de confirmer la disposition de la location pour le\n"
"Asset suivant:\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Nom de l'actif:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('acte') ou not_available\"> </t>\n"
"Date de début de location:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('start_date') ou not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Date de fin de location:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('end_date') ou not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Selon l'accord, veuillez assurer le paiement en temps opportun des frais de location et adhérer aux conditions\n"
"décrit là-bas.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Si vous avez des questions ou nécessitez des clarifications supplémentaires concernant le bail\n"
"Accord, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter à votre convenance.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Si vous avez des questions ou si vous avez besoin d'une aide supplémentaire, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Cordialement,\n"
"<br>\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>"

#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_leased_assent_return_reminder
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding:0px;\">\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('customer') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    This is a friendly reminder regarding the return of the leased asset,\n"
"                    <b>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    </b>\n"
"                    , which is due\n"
"                    for return as per our lease agreement on\n"
"                    <b>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"ctx.get('end_date') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    </b>\n"
"                    .\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Please ensure that the asset is returned on or before the specified return date to avoid any\n"
"                    potential late fees or penalties as outlined in our agreement.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div style = \"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"<div>\n"
"Cher\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('client') ou not_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ceci est un rappel amical concernant le retour de l'actif loué,\n"
"<b>\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('actif') ou not_available\">, </t>\n"
"</b>\n"
", qui est dû\n"
"pour le retour conformément à notre contrat de location sur\n"
"<b>\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('end_date') ou not_available\">, </t>\n"
"</b>\n"
".\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Veuillez vous assurer que l'actif est renvoyé le plus ou avant la date de retour spécifiée pour éviter tout\n"
"Frais ou pénalités potentiels tels que décrits dans notre accord.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Si vous avez des questions ou avez besoin d'aide supplémentaire, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Cordialement,\n"
"<br>\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>"

#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_assent_rental_invoice_due_reminder
msgid ""
"<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding:0px;\">\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('customer') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    This is a friendly reminder regarding the upcoming payment for the rental asset invoice.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    As per our agreement, the payment for the asset\n"
"                    <b>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    </b>is due on\n"
"                    <b><t t-out=\"ctx.get('due_date') or not_available\">,</t></b>\n"
"                    . However, it appears that\n"
"                    the payment has not yet been received.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Please ensure that the payment is made promptly to avoid any late fees or disruptions to your rental\n"
"                    agreement. Your cooperation in this matter is greatly appreciated.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have already made the payment, please disregard this reminder, and kindly inform us of the\n"
"                    transaction details for our records.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div style = \"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">\n"
"<div>\n"
"Cher\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('client') ou not_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Ceci est un rappel amical concernant le paiement à venir de la facture des actifs de location.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Selon notre accord, le paiement de l'actif\n"
"<b>\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('actif') ou not_available\">, </t>\n"
"</b> est dû sur\n"
"<b> <t t-out = \"ctx.get ('dû_date') ou not_available\">, </t> </b>\n"
".Cependant, il semble que\n"
"Le paiement n'a pas encore été reçu.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Veuillez vous assurer que le paiement est effectué rapidement pour éviter tout frais ou perturbation en retard à votre location\n"
"accord.Votre coopération dans cette affaire est grandement appréciée.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Si vous avez déjà effectué le paiement, veuillez ignorer ce rappel et veuillez nous informer de la\n"
"Détails de la transaction pour nos enregistrements.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Si vous avez des questions ou avez besoin d'aide supplémentaire, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Cordialement,\n"
"<br>\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>"

#. module: cyllo_asset_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:cyllo_asset_management.mail_template_asset_assignment
msgid ""
"<div>\n"
"                <div>\n"
"                    Dear\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('employee') or not_available\">,</t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    I hope this email finds you well.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    I am pleased to inform you that the following asset have been assigned to you:\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Asset Name:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('asset') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Assign Date:\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"ctx.get('assign_date') or not_available\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Please take good care of the assigned asset and ensure they are used responsibly in accordance\n"
"                    with our organization's policies and guidelines.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Should you encounter any issues or have any\n"
"                    questions regarding the assigned asset, please feel free to reach out to us for assistance.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us.\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"\n"
"                </div>\n"
"            </div>\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"<div>\n"
"<div>\n"
"Cher\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('employee') ou not_available\">, </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"J'espère que cet e-mail vous trouve bien.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Je suis heureux de vous informer que l'actif suivant vous a été affecté:\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Nom de l'actif:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('acte') ou not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Date d'attribution:\n"
"<t t-out = \"ctx.get ('attox_date') ou not_available\"> </t>\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Veuillez prendre bien soin de l'actif attribué et assurez-vous qu'ils sont utilisés de manière responsable en fonction\n"
"avec les politiques et directives de notre organisation.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Si vous rencontrez des problèmes ou avez-vous\n"
"Questions concernant l'actif attribué, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter pour obtenir de l'aide.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Si vous avez des questions ou si vous avez besoin d'une aide supplémentaire, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter.\n"
"<br>\n"
"<br>\n"
"Cordialement,\n"
"<br>\n"
"\n"
"</div>\n"
"</div>"

